-- Exxon Mobil Closes Oso Platform in Nigeria After Attack and Abductions
-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 2010-11-16T14:38:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-16/exxon-mobil-closes-oso-platform-in-nigeria-after-attack.html
Exxon Mobil Corp. closed its Oso gas
and condensate platform in Nigeria as a precaution after an
attack yesterday saw eight employees kidnapped, the company said
in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
